title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H3 – Aug 3 2022
itunes:title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H3 – Aug 3 2022
description:
GOP gubernatorial nominee Tudor Dixon joins Buck fresh off her primary victory to explain what it's going take to defeat Michigan Governor Gretchen Whitmer, who used to keep pillows with Fauci's face on them behind her during TV interviews. DeSantis tells The View to go pound Florida sand. Kim Iversen talks to Buck about leaving The Hill's Rising over being barred from Fauci interview. The Dog Days of Summer at ClayAndBuck.com. Peaky Blinders and flat wool caps.

Follow Clay & Buck on YouTube: https://www.youtube.com/c/clayandbuck
